## Tiered Workflow (S/A/B/C)

All tiers: branch + PR + tests + lint + security. Tier sets the ceremony level.

| Tier | Scope | Ceremony | Review |
|------|-------|----------|--------|
| **S** | Schema, security, infra, auth, deploy | Issue > analysis > ADR > plan > implement > record | Human required |
| **A** | New endpoint, service, model, integration | Issue > plan > implement > record | Human required |
| **B** | Modify existing endpoint, logging, filters | Implement > record | Auto-merge if green |
| **C** | Docs, comments, typos | Implement | Auto-merge if green |

Conventional commits required: `feat|fix|docs|refactor|test|chore|ci|perf: description`

Details, ticket creation, and ceremony steps: `.github/instructions/workflow.md`

